{
  "stem": "8072.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was actually, right after the war, I was the only one that-- you know, whatever you did was illegal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To eat-- anything you did was illegal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if I got caught it was bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But otherwise, I used to like use the horse and buggy to transport some flowers to this, and this to that, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mahel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my other brother, which was Dovet-- and they were-- he came back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was in a prisoner camp for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then he came back, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, we lived there at-- in home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time-- whatever you-- they still were going some kind little business, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't-- you weren't supposed to do nothing, but you're still doing something, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, they were constantly-- they were constantly rounding up eligible people for work camps, to send you here, to send you there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So basically, you didn't go for walks in the street, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you had to do something, you did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you were in constant awareness that you're not supposed to be outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're not supposed to do this, or you're not supposed to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was the one camp, at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other camps, actually, we didn't know until was actually sent away till-- till your sent-- till liquidated and sent to one of the camps, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a lot of work, that if they caught you, even if they didn't send you to camp, they had some work in town, around the town.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Have-- you know-- took you for a week or two weeks, and do some physical labor, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
